WEBVTT

00:02:55.920 --> 00:03:00.896
In Philadelphia, before losing the rematch
the following year in New York.

00:03:00.920 --> 00:03:02.680
But I guess that's fair.

00:03:04.320 --> 00:03:09.416
There is no day in history,
special calendar entry

00:03:09.440 --> 00:03:12.936
for all the people
who failed to climb Mt. Everest

00:03:12.960 --> 00:03:15.696
before Sir Edmund Hillary
and Tenzing Norgay

00:03:15.720 --> 00:03:16.920
made it to the top.

00:03:17.960 --> 00:03:21.720
And in 1997, I was still
the world champion

00:03:24.520 --> 00:03:28.720
when chess computers finally came of age.

00:03:29.520 --> 00:03:31.496
I was Mt. Everest,